data.description:
This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house offers comfort, convenience, and a touch of Florida elegance. It offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, allowing you to experience the best of Haines City living. Don't miss out on this opportunity schedule a viewing today and make this house your new home!

This 12-month lease agreement, typical of the Sunshine State, requires the first and last month's rent at signing, strictly prohibits smoking anywhere on the property to comply with Florida's Smoke-Free Workplace Act, allows small pets (under 20 pounds) with a non-refundable pet deposit of $250. The tenant is responsible for utilities, including water, electricity, and internet, lawn care, etc. Additionally, please be aware that, according to Florida law, a 60-day notice is required for lease termination.
